snippet.title: AEW Fight Forever | Dynamite Featuring The Acclaimed DLC Available Now!
snippet.description:
#aewfightforever #theacclaimed 

YO! LISTEN! The wait is finally over! The Acclaimed have arrived in Season 2 of #AEWFightForever! Dynamite featuring The Acclaimed DLC is available for download on XBOX, PlayStation and PC today! Nintendo Switch to follow.

The golden era of wrestling games is back! AEW: Fight Forever is available now on your favorite console and PC! Buy it now! - https://aew.thqnordic.com/

SUBSCRIBE now and never miss a new video:
@aew @aewshorts @aewgames @aewmusic @aewpodcasts  

• AEW Dynamite airs every Wednesday night 8e/7c on TBS
• AEW Rampage airs every Friday night 10e/9c on TNT
• AEW Collision airs every Saturday at 8e/7c on TNT
